---

<EdukasiLayout {...pageData}>
  <div class="space-y-10">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-600 to-sky-800 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,')] opacity-20"></div>
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Hukum dalam Khotbah Yesus</h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-sky-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-6">
          Penggenapan dan Pendalaman Hukum Taurat dalam Khotbah di Bukit
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mt-8">
          <span class="bg-sky-500/30 backdrop-blur-sm text-sky-100 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">
            Matius 5-7
          </span>
          <span class="bg-sky-500/30 backdrop-blur-sm text-sky-100 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">
            Khotbah di Bukit
          </span>
          <span class="bg-sky-500/30 backdrop-blur-sm text-sky-100 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">
            Penggenapan Hukum Taurat
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Introduction Section -->
    <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-10 border border-sky-100">
      <div class="flex items-start mb-6">
        <div class="bg-sky-100 p-3 rounded-full mr-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-sky-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Revolusi Moral Kerajaan Allah</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yesus Menggenapi dan Memperdalam Makna Hukum Taurat</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">
        <p class="text-lg">
          <strong>Khotbah di Bukit</strong> (Matius 5-7) merupakan pengajaran Yesus yang paling komprehensif tentang 
          hubungan antara hukum Taurat dan kehidupan dalam Kerajaan Allah. Di sini, Yesus tidak hanya menegaskan otoritas hukum Taurat, 
          tetapi juga <strong>menggenapi</strong> dan <strong>memperdalam</strong> maknanya, membawa revolusi moral yang mengubah 
          fokus dari ketaatan eksternal ke transformasi internal.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-sky-50 border-l-4 border-sky-500 p-6 my-6 rounded-r-lg">
          <p class="text-sky-800 font-medium mb-2">Kontekstualisasi Historis</p>
          <p class="text-sky-700">
            Yesus berbicara dalam konteks dimana hukum Taurat sering direduksi menjadi legalisme eksternal oleh para ahli Taurat dan orang Farisi. 
            Khotbah di Bukit merupakan koreksi terhadap penyimpangan ini dan restorasi makna sejati hukum Allah.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">Struktur Khotbah di Bukit</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-6">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-50 to-white border border-sky-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <div class="bg-sky-100 w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <span class="text-sky-600 font-bold">1</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Ucapan Bahagia</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Nilai-nilai Kerajaan Allah (Matius 5:3-12)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-50 to-white border border-sky-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <div class="bg-sky-100 w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <span class="text-sky-600 font-bold">2</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Penggenapan Hukum</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Antitesis dan pendalaman (Matius 5:17-48)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-50 to-white border border-sky-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <div class="bg-sky-100 w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <span class="text-sky-600 font-bold">3</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Hidup dalam Kerajaan</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Aplikasi praktis (Matius 6-7)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Sermon Sections -->
    <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-10 border border-sky-100">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Bagian Utama Khotbah tentang Hukum</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Tiga pilar utama pengajaran Yesus tentang penggenapan hukum Taurat
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        {sermonSections.map((section, index) => (
          <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-sky-50 border border-sky-100 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-start gap-6">
              <!-- Icon and Number -->
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                  <div class="bg-sky-100 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-sky-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d={section.icon}></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <span class="bg-sky-500 text-white text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Bagian {index + 1}</span>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-2">{section.title}</h3>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Content -->
              <div class="flex-grow">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 mb-4 border border-sky-100">
                  <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 italic mb-2">"{section.content}"</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-sky-600 font-semibold">{section.scripture}</p>
                </div>
                
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">{section.explanation}</p>
                
                <div class="bg-sky-50 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sky-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Implikasi Praktis
                  </h4>
                  <ul class="space-y-2">
                    {section.applications.map((app) => (
                      <li class="flex items-start text-gray-600 text-sm">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sky-500 mr-2 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                        </svg>
                        {app}
                      </li>
                    ))}
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Antitheses Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-600 to-sky-800 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 text-white">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-10">Enam Antitesis Yesus</h2>
        <p class="text-sky-100 text-center mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          "Kamu telah mendengar firman kepada nenek moyang kita... tetapi Aku berkata kepadamu" - 
          Yesus memperdalam dan menggenapi hukum Taurat dengan otoritas Mesianik
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-left">
          {antitheses.map((antithesis, index) => (
            <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 hover:bg-white/15 transition-all duration-300">
              <div class="flex items-start mb-4">
                <div class="bg-white/20 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 flex-shrink-0">
                  <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">{index + 1}</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">{antithesis.oldLaw}</h3>
                  <p class="text-sky-100 text-sm italic">{antithesis.reference}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-lg p-4 mb-3">
                <p class="text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-1">"Tetapi Aku berkata kepadamu:"</p>
                <p class="text-sky-100 text-sm">{antithesis.newTeaching}</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="flex items-start text-sky-100 text-xs">
                  <span><strong>Fokus:</strong> {antithesis.focus}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start text-sky-100 text-xs">
                  <span><strong>Implikasi:</strong> {antithesis.implication}</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Theological Implications -->
    <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-10 border border-sky-100">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Implikasi Teologis</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Makna mendalam dari penggenapan hukum Taurat oleh Yesus
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {theologicalImplications.map((implication) => (
          <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-sky-50 border border-sky-100 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sky-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
              </svg>
              {implication.title}
            </h3>
            
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">{implication.description}</p>
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3 border border-sky-100 mb-3">
              <p class="text-sky-600 font-semibold text-sm">{implication.scripture}</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-sky-50 rounded-lg p-3">
              <p class="text-sky-700 text-sm font-medium">Signifikansi: {implication.significance}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-amber-800 mb-2">Otoritas Mesianik Yesus</h4>
        <p class="text-amber-700">
          Ketika Yesus berkata "Tetapi Aku berkata kepadamu", Ia menegaskan otoritas yang setara dengan Allah. 
          Ini bukan sekadar interpretasi baru tentang Taurat, tetapi penyataan otoritas Mesianik untuk 
          menetapkan makna sejati dan penggenapan hukum Taurat.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Practical Applications -->
    <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-10 border border-sky-100">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Penerapan dalam Kehidupan Kristen</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Bagaimana hidup menurut standar Kerajaan Allah yang diajarkan Yesus
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-sky-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sky-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Transformasi Hati</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Fokus pada perubahan internal, bukan hanya eksternal</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-sky-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sky-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Integritas Total</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Keselarasan antara pikiran, perkataan, dan perbuatan</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-sky-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sky-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Rekonsiliasi</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Memulihkan hubungan sebelum menyembah</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-sky-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sky-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Ketergantungan pada Anugerah</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Mengakui kebutuhan akan kuasa Allah untuk taat</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-500 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-green-800 mb-2">Keseimbangan yang Alkitabiah</h4>
